{
  "id": "603ba29c90bc5b001c018bb9",
  "title": "Scrapboxのpresentation mode",
  "created": 1614520990,
  "updated": 1725036923,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "603ba29c90bc5b001c018bb9",
      "text": "Scrapboxのpresentation mode",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614520990,
      "updated": 1614520990
    },
    {
      "id": "603ba2cde5172d0000e4a7d9",
      "text": "\t[Page Menu]→[Start presentation]で開始",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1614521036,
      "updated": 1646400188
    },
    {
      "id": "603ba431e5172d0000e4a7de",
      "text": "\t\tEscで終了",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614521393,
      "updated": 1614521401
    },
    {
      "id": "603ba29fe5172d0000e4a7d6",
      "text": "\t表示のしくみがよく分かっていない[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614520990,
      "updated": 1614521422
    },
    {
      "id": "603ba2aee5172d0000e4a7d8",
      "text": "\t\t思ったのと違う感じで表示されることがある",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614521005,
      "updated": 1614521018
    },
    {
      "id": "637b4f5b7838e30000f91fa4",
      "text": "\t#プレゼンテーションモード",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1669025628,
      "updated": 1669025641
    },
    {
      "id": "637b4f597838e30000f91fa3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1669025625,
      "updated": 1669025625
    },
    {
      "id": "603ba344e5172d0000e4a7dd",
      "text": "表示のしくみ",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614521155,
      "updated": 1614521441
    },
    {
      "id": "603be6c5e5172d00006ce6b3",
      "text": "\t>[プレゼンモード]は実は通常のエディタの見た目をCSSで切り替えているだけ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1614538438,
      "updated": 1669025647
    },
    {
      "id": "603beb2ae5172d00006ce722",
      "text": "  > 同じDOM・Reactコンポーネントを使いまわしている",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614539563,
      "updated": 1614539570
    },
    {
      "id": "603beb2ae5172d00006ce723",
      "text": "  > navbarやテロメアが無いのはCSSで非表示にしているだけ",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614539563,
      "updated": 1614539570
    },
    {
      "id": "603bea88e5172d00006ce71e",
      "text": "\t\t[/shokai/Scrapboxのプレゼンモードの表示切り替えのしくみ]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614539401,
      "updated": 1614539401
    },
    {
      "id": "603be914e5172d00006ce6b4",
      "text": "\t\t[presentation mode用CSS]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614539028,
      "updated": 1614539049
    },
    {
      "id": "603ba315e5172d0000e4a7da",
      "text": " インデントレベル0の[見出し行]に続いて箇条書きしたものをブロックとして、空行区切りで並べると、各ブロックがスライドのページになる？",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614521108,
      "updated": 1614540122
    },
    {
      "id": "603bea69e5172d00006ce717",
      "text": " \t>プレゼンモード内のページは内部的には`section`と呼ばれている",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614539370,
      "updated": 1614539373
    },
    {
      "id": "603bea6de5172d00006ce718",
      "text": "  >sectionのtitleには`.section-title`というcss class nameが付く",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614539373,
      "updated": 1614539380
    },
    {
      "id": "603bedcbe5172d00006ce728",
      "text": "  \t[/shokai/プレゼンモードをページめくりではなく縦スクロールにする]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614540235,
      "updated": 1614540236
    },
    {
      "id": "603beaf1e5172d00006ce721",
      "text": "   presentation modeじゃなくてもあるやつだ[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614539506,
      "updated": 1614539517
    },
    {
      "id": "603bed64e5172d00006ce724",
      "text": "  sectionが切り替わる条件？",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614540132,
      "updated": 1614540168
    },
    {
      "id": "603bed7ae5172d00006ce725",
      "text": "  \t空行の後にインデントレベル0の行が現れると、新しいsectionとして認識される？[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614540155,
      "updated": 1614540229
    },
    {
      "id": "6040b058e5172d0000dc03c1",
      "text": "  \t既存のページに追記して、追記行以下のsectionの構造が変わった場合、ページ遷移やReloadをしないと反映されない",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614852184,
      "updated": 1614852288
    },
    {
      "id": "6040b92775892100002aa1ac",
      "text": "  [/neet]はセクションを可視化している",
      "userId": "60226bcd2fbabe0022758921",
      "created": 1614854439,
      "updated": 1614854509
    },
    {
      "id": "6040cadfe5172d000032534b",
      "text": "  \tあの番号はsectionだったのかー[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614858973,
      "updated": 1614858982
    },
    {
      "id": "60ce9d7a79d3a90000398f5c",
      "text": "  \tへぇ[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1624153467,
      "updated": 1624153469
    },
    {
      "id": "603ba33be5172d0000e4a7dc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614521147,
      "updated": 1614521147
    },
    {
      "id": "603ba4c0e5172d0000e4a7df",
      "text": "スライド表示を意図して作られているページの例",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614521537,
      "updated": 1614521578
    },
    {
      "id": "603ba4c2e5172d0000e4a7e1",
      "text": "　[/ScrapboxHelp/Scrapboxチュートリアルスライド]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614521539,
      "updated": 1614521539
    },
    {
      "id": "60caaac3e5172d00009e2ce2",
      "text": "　[/zmz-rcgs2021]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1623894723,
      "updated": 1623894724
    },
    {
      "id": "603ba4c1e5172d0000e4a7e0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614521539,
      "updated": 1614521539
    },
    {
      "id": "603ba4cde5172d0000e4a7e2",
      "text": "関連UserScript/UserCSS",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614521550,
      "updated": 1614521550
    },
    {
      "id": "603beac5e5172d00006ce720",
      "text": " [/shokai/プレゼンモードをページめくりではなく縦スクロールにする]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614539461,
      "updated": 1614539462
    },
    {
      "id": "603ba4cee5172d0000e4a7e3",
      "text": "\t[/customize/presentation modeで各スライドタイトルの文字色を変更]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614521550,
      "updated": 1614521550
    },
    {
      "id": "603ba4cfe5172d0000e4a7e4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614521552,
      "updated": 1614521552
    },
    {
      "id": "603be4bbe5172d00006ce6af",
      "text": "プレゼンするのはScrapboxの役割なのか？",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614537914,
      "updated": 1614537924
    },
    {
      "id": "603be4c5e5172d00006ce6b1",
      "text": "　[/suto3/忍び寄る機能主義]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1614537924,
      "updated": 1614537941
    },
    {
      "id": "603be4bee5172d00006ce6b0",
